{"tid":619551,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚每日都要做嘅事","createTime":"2018-04-06T17:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T18:56:02.000Z","uid":20914,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b88796c7da3a50acfe28cdfa53b5f04e666c7df3","tid":619551,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:42:57.000Z","msg":"喺生活之中，久唔久都會有啲事幫助我哋建立自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然機會唔多，但係日積月累起上嚟，無形間都會令毒撚增加咗自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為咗避免呢種情況發生，我覺得毒撚每日都應該照五分鐘鏡，清除不必要嘅自信，噉先對自己有益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb17ea3a7516fb7185be402c74227f160ea5dc5a","tid":619551,"uid":57308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:43:47.000Z","msg":"呢段垃圾你打左幾耐？"},{"pid":"87917f29bc00c3af4794955f3c4918a5d70a8ccd","tid":619551,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:06:24.000Z","msg":"毒撚屋企從來都冇鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85778ecb66b24bf5478c8ef522e1e76d61593c3","tid":619551,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"87917f29bc00c3af4794955f3c4918a5d70a8ccd","tid":619551,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:06:24.000Z","msg":"毒撚屋企從來都冇鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該有啲嘢喺度提醒自己"},{"pid":"3e94bcf5e6a336f14c413029a516e8a2de77770b","tid":619551,"uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:56:02.000Z","msg":"可唔可以做啲有意義嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 